{"tid":867850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女教師合照「溢出滿滿母愛」　網暴動：前方同學被撞暈啦","createTime":"2018-10-19T04:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T07:39:24.000Z","uid":19762,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"54b8f4313a337f16ccb4152210064552b9cddd0c","tid":867850,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=444449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D444449&h=eeba01eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n都說「男生是視覺的動物」但沒想到連小朋友也不例外，日前香港特首林鄭月娥訪問一處小學，就在一張學校老師、小朋友的合照中，一名女老師意外成為亮點，這名女老師不僅「上圍」有看頭，就連坐在前方的學生也忍不住出現「謎之笑容」。<br />\n<br />\n據《nmplus》報導，香港特首林鄭月娥12日前往深水埗的英華小學參觀，了解學生進行課外活動的情況，並與師生合照留念，據了解由於林鄭月娥在當地民望並不算好，網路上只要有相關訊息，通常回應都不好，然而這張照片，讓網友全改觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/19/1597802-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F1597802-XXL.jpg&h=9875df3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港,正妹,巨乳,性感,老師,女教師　圖／翻攝自臉書 ID-1597802<br />\n<br />\n▲圖／翻攝自臉書<br />\n<br />\n只見照片中，除了特首林鄭月娥與小朋友外，一名身穿灰色上衣的女老師意外成為焦點，只見這位女老師「澎湃的母愛」，就連前方的男同學都忍不住回頭，畫面相當耐人尋味。而這名女老師余靜韻也因此爆紅，對此，許多網友紛紛表示「想回去念小學了」、「好大」、「林鄭終於做對一件事了」、「撞暈這個四眼同學啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/19/1597805-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F1597805-XXL.jpg&h=eced36b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港,正妹,巨乳,性感,老師,女教師　▲圖／翻攝自臉書 ID-1597805<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/19/1597806-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F1597806-XXL.jpg&h=9b73e443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港,正妹,巨乳,性感,老師,女教師　▲圖／翻攝自臉書 ID-1597806<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/19/1597807-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F1597807-XXL.jpg&h=00d6a82c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港,正妹,巨乳,性感,老師,女教師　▲圖／翻攝自臉書 ID-1597807"},{"pid":"accd476bd6044402110a9d3a8b76ca4eed4b80fd","tid":867850,"uid":23236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:02:32.000Z","msg":"放開個細路！"},{"pid":"b60b256b17d4cff9f04e34f10665017115482df3","tid":867850,"uid":71218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"紅到台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出度做KOL吧啦"},{"pid":"c889554a67f3aad659d2b195a8a53641de4b3ace","tid":867850,"uid":5475,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:08:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大陸中心／綜合報導</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"25fa6cb7c6a741e0a7a4237159aa7d7e1204baf6","tid":867850,"uid":208292,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"香港,正妹,巨乳,性感,老師,女教師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4dfc907cc1233f71606810a8c855ab491121b6c","tid":867850,"uid":148874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33358f6a12ae010e592a76320c2c805d1c25942","tid":867850,"uid":156511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:30:14.000Z","msg":"台妹： 哈，咁都上新聞"},{"pid":"ea6435bc10018cca3a5de9095338a2069a29553a","tid":867850,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25fa6cb7